    "description": "ELEMENTS, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, provides data-based personal authentication and optimization solutions as backend-as-a-service to service providers across various industries in Japan. The company offers LIQUID eKYC and Polarise eKYC, an online identity verification service; LIQUID Auth, an authentication service; PASS, a digital identity wallet; GPASS, a digital ID wallet for foreigners; office diagnostic report, which is a digital transformation service for office relocation and renovation; MyPlace for Home, a smart home/smart city platform; my IDEAL, a size matching service; Coordware, a personalized marketing for E-Commerce using generative AI; ELEMENTS cloud, a GPU cloud for AI development; and AiQ PERMISSION, an AI automatic refueling permit monitoring system. It also engages in the research and development of image recognition engines and data analysis platforms; offers optimization service for office living environment and biometric authentication service; and engages in construction of cloud environment construction and data center operation business, as well as engages in healthcare, web advertising, and medical supply business. ELEMENTS, Inc. was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
